thread.title: Glenn Johnson
thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Glenn Johnson

author: Glenn Johnson
title: Glenn Johnson
text: My wife and I took our parrot to Ocean County Veterinary Hospital for the first time recently. The facilities are very clean and the staff knowledgeable and professional. They were very kind to and gentle with our bird. I would recommend them to any bird owner.
